node.areas_of_interest_freeform: We know that climate is about more than carbonits also about force multipliers like asset finance and distribution. We believe the best climate solutions dont look like climate solutions at all, just better, faster, and cheaper products and services. We prefer rapid deployment that will get us close to 1.5C in warming while upgrading our systems to make them more resilient. But well also look at moonshot opportunities because we know we need a plan B.

node.areas_of_interest_freeform: Were looking to work with Israeli-led, pre-seed start-ups from all industries that want to grow their company in the US market. We invest $150K in each company and selectively accept 6-9 teams every 6 months to go through our intensive go-to-market and mentorship-driven program. node.areas_of_interest_freeform:
Cloud and Data Center Infrastructure, consumer data/content services, mobile and connected devices, AR/VR, Industrial IoT, ML/AI.

Western Digital Capital partners with innovative startups that improve how data is generated, saved, managed, and consumed. We provide the capital, expertise and connections required to scale the organizations of tomorrow

Startups need to bring new strategic value for Western Digital.

node.person.name: Errol Damelin
node.areas_of_interest_freeform:
I'm a serial entrepreneur and active angel investor. I live in London but invest globally, usually at pre-seed and seed. 

Having founded and run Wonga to annual profitability of over $100 million, Fintech is my natural base but I also invest in related branded consumer offerings, decisioning systems, AI, crypto, blockchain, insurance, property tech and digital health.

Im lucky enough to have invested early and helped the founders of Transferwise, CityMapper, Nested, Habito and PurpleBricks
